		  "text": "[b]NEW TASK DETECTED[/b]\n\nBLUEPRINT REQUIREMENTS INCOMPLETE\n\nSUGGESTED ACTIONS\n\n1. Navigate to nearby resource nodes.\n\n2. Scan objects to determine composition.\n\n3. Mine required resources.\n\n4. Return resources for fabrication.\n\n---\n\n[b]NAVIGATION[/b]\n\nThe Auto Pilot can route to known targets.\n\n---\n\n[b]SCAN[/b]\n\nScanning reveals information about objects, contacts, and resources.\n\n---\n\n[b]MINING[/b]\n\nAsteroids may contain usable materials.\n\nRequired materials can be collected and stored in inventory.",
